"Narrated Ibn `Abbas:Regarding the Verse: \"And among men is he who worships Allah's as it were on the very edge.\" (22.11). A man used to come to Medina and if his wife brought a son and his mares produces offspring, he would say, \"This religion (Islam) is good,\" but if his wife did not give birth to a child and his mares produced no offspring, he would say, \"This religion is bad"